name: G & F Building contractors Ltd
tag_list: conservatories, extensions, windows, doors, diy, caprentry, plastering, fencing, decorating, petitions, tarmac, driveways, guttering, fascia
overview:
Over the years G&F Building Contractors Ltd have built a reputation of supplying not only quality workmanship but a customer care that is second to none. We have worked for many schools, churches, councils and private customers, on projects ranging from £500.00 up to £100,000.

Our representatives are friendly experienced people that are there to help and advise you. If we feel you need extra advice or guidance, we will arrange a meeting for you with our architect so you can discuss your requirements in as much detail as needed. All quotes and advice are provided for free with no obligation or hard sale.
